<h5>Problem solving through design</h5>
<p>Based on the needs and goals of my audience, I decided to created an app which would be a single source of information on gluten free food products, recipes and restaurants. Creating this on an application platform will allow users to access information, easily, quickly and whilst on the move - something which would contribute to solving a key problem; the time take it takes to access information.</p>
<p>Following this decision, I sketched out the user journey through defining; user, task and goal.</p>
