<h5>Reflection</h5>
<p>This app solves the main problems that users reported through a simple and effective design.</p> 
<p>Creating one single source of information, where users are able to find gluten free restaurants, food items and recipes solves the key problem of many sources of information to navigate. Creating this on an application platform allows for a reduction in the time taken to find the information, thus solving the second the critical problem for users.</p> 
<p>To further develop this design, I would like to encompass purchasing functions allowing users to create a basket and purchase food items directly from the app. Additionally, I believe it would be valuable to add a meal planner function, linking to purchasing the food items allowing users to complete all desired tasks in one place - ensuring an effective user experience. </p>



